[menu m_elem_general]
One can ONLY possess the powers of the 5 super elementals.  The weaker elements are not strong enough to generate elemental shards.  Legends tells that the shards can be found somewhere deep in Halix.  

on=0 More
SRC.ITEMMENU m_elem_general2

[menu m_elem_general2]
This powerful forger was created by High Mage Jaxis.  It's magic was so powerful that it corrupted Jaxis with greed and anger.  Be wary, the power of the super elements are not to be taken lightly.

on=0 Done
SRC.ITEMMENU m_elem_forger

[menu m_elem_lightning]
Lightning is an extremely powerful element.  It's electric power flows through everything it touches; devouring its foes and protecting its master.

on=0 Done
SRC.ITEMMENU m_elem_forger

[menu m_elem_venom]
Venom is a corrosive and toxic element.  It's able to destroy the smallest orc or the biggest dragon with its powerful toxin.

on=0 Done
SRC.ITEMMENU m_elem_forger

[menu m_elem_lava]
Lava is a slow, but powerful, fiery element.  It's extremely destructive, covering everything in blazing, molten rock.

on=0 Done
SRC.ITEMMENU m_elem_forger

[menu m_elem_Death]
Not very much is known about Death.  One can possess the power of darkness and stealth, along with deceit and greed if death is their master.  

on=0 Done
SRC.ITEMMENU m_elem_forger

[menu m_elem_plant]
Plant is the very power that holds the Earth together.  Plant is mainly defensive, protecting its master with the power of the Earth.

on=0 Done
SRC.ITEMMENU m_elem_forger



